{"word":"στέφος","slug":"στέφος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στέφος</b></el> <el>(στέφος, ος, εος, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:στέφω'><el>στέφω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a crown, wreath, garland</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <el>στέφη,  στέμματα</el>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of libations, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}